{"tid":1657802,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"林鄭果然係好歹毒，一招九成收香港人皮","createTime":"2019-10-16T09:04:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T09:52:51.000Z","uid":161430,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f924b7ec6d57c66b0d78fc161c1e9335095fc607","tid":1657802,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:04:20.000Z","msg":"九成按揭，樓價推高，既得利益者、有樓者贏，<br />\n地產商一定護住林鄭個政府。<br />\n<br />\n後生既，睇唔清自己能力，借九成再供到跳樓，<br />\n你要做浮屍，你死你事，因為你後生。<br />\n<br />\n本來想做8成去上樓，3 40歲既人，慢慢儲夠首期，<br />\n點知又比林鄭呢下推高樓價，追唔切增幅，<br />\n上倒樓變上唔倒，或者加入埋做九成按揭敢死隊，<br />\n最後又係你死你事。<br />\n<br />\n最後香港既得利益者贏，150人贏，其他人輸，<br />\n死供緊樓既人又唔敢抗爭，<br />\n香港人唔買 價錢貴到癲既樓，唔緊要，<br />\n仲有另一個贏家：一堆點都走嚟買下既大陸佬<br />\n<br />\n一招收大部分香港人皮，佢除左毒，又根本唔傻<br />\n咩仇都報曬啦今舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"195856f6763dcc42981060b030193b0fe141d09e","tid":1657802,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eLY27V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eLY27V.jpg&h=0bfc2f6e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0a462bdb2624f4e1a34c5f7a7e544e4380c9c3c0","tid":1657802,"uid":161430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"195856f6763dcc42981060b030193b0fe141d09e","tid":1657802,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:05:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eLY27V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eLY27V.jpg&h=0bfc2f6e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:06:18.000Z","msg":"20號大家記住去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20739d76dd466485144fcbf144626a6c5600cd00","tid":1657802,"uid":124372,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:09:54.000Z","msg":"就係供三十年已經笑撚死我<br />\n香港已經無法治<br />\n政府部門得幾個未崩塌<br />\n醫管局、消費者委員會、rthk電視